Vectors
nets or reg data types can be declared as vectors
by default its 1 bit

wire a; //scalar net variable, default
wire [7:0] bus //8 bit bus
wire [31: 0] busA, busB, busC //3 buses of 32 bit width
31 is the msb
0 is the lsb
reg [0:40] virtual addr; //0 is msb, 40th is the lsb

eg:
CASE I
reg [7:0] A;
A=8'b10110011;
Index: 7 6 5 4 3 2 1 0
Value: 1 0 1 1 0 0 1 1
A[2] = 0
A[3:0] = 0 0 1 1
A[0:3] = not possible (because the vector was declared descending part selects must also be same)

CASE II
reg [0:7] B;
B=8'b10110011
Index: 0 1 2 3 4 5 6 7
Value: 1 0 1 1 0 0 1 1
B[2]=1
B[0:3]= 1 0 1 1
B[3:0] = not possible














